[tool_call: run_shell_command for downloading the server JAR]
Server JAR downloaded. Let me register it as a managed service and start it.
[tool_call: service_manage with action 'register', name 'minecraft', command 'java -Xmx2G -jar server.jar nogui']
[tool_call: service_manage with action 'start', name 'minecraft']
